Yawan masu kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) ya karu sosai a Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Idan aka yi la'akari da cewa duk mutanen da ke fama da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) suna nuna alamun cutar iri ɗaya a cikin Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila, hakan yana nuna cewa, kodayake akwai bambance-bambance a cikin yanayin ƙasa zuwa ƙasa, cutar COVID-19 tana yaduwa cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Dangane da abubuwan da suka faru a Italiya, ƙasashe, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa da gaggawa suna buƙatar kasancewa cikin shiri don karɓar ƙarin masu cutar COVID-19 waɗanda ke buƙatar kulawa ta musamman, musamman a cikin ICU.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an gano mutane da yawa da ke fama da cutar numfashi a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga Janairun 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta bayyana cewa cutar ta samo asali ne daga wani sabon nau'in kwayar cutar coronavirus wanda yanzu ake kira SARS-CoV-2.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ke haifar da SARS-CoV-2 an kira ta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Bayanai da muke da su a yanzu sun nuna cewa kashi 80% na mutanen da ke da cutar COVID-19 suna da yanayin rashin lafiya mai sauƙi, kamar rashin lafiya na numfashi ko kuma wahalar numfashi, kuma yawancin su suna rayuwa.
A cikin kashi 14 cikin ɗari na mutane, COVID-19 yana haifar da rashin lafiya mai tsanani wanda ke buƙatar asibiti, yayin da kashi 6 cikin ɗari ke haifar da rashin lafiya mai tsanani wanda ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Yawan mutuwar da ke faruwa a asibiti saboda COVID-19 ya kai kashi 4 cikin ɗari.
A cikin wannan binciken, za a bincika yanayin COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a cikin Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila (UK) kuma a kwatanta shi da na lardin Hubei, China.
Za mu kuma kwatanta yawan sabbin cututtukan COVID-19 a cikin Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila da Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
An samu wasu cututtukan COVID-19 a Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila
Kamar yadda ya faru a China, COVID-19 ya bazu zuwa wasu ƙasashe kuma cutar COVID-19 tana yaduwa a wasu ƙasashe kamar yadda ta faru a wannan ƙasar.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Babban Daraktan Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin cutar da ke yaduwa.
A ranar 5 ga Maris, rahoton Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri da abokan aikinsa, sun ba da rahoton farkon yanayin COVID-19 na Turai bisa ga ma'anar WHO.
A cikin Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai, an fara samun wasu mutane uku a Faransa a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020; an dawo da su daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an sami wasu cututtukan COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashe 30 na Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila (UK), kuma daga 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an sami ƙididdigar kamuwa da cutar 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727 tare da aƙalla 17,750 a Italiya da mutuwar 1,441.
Samun cikakken adadin mutane da suka kamu da COVID-19
Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), ta sabunta ƙididdigar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa, wanda kawai ya dogara da tushen hukuma kamar ma'aikatun kiwon lafiya na duniya, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki da WHO, kowace rana da ƙarfe 8 na safe.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanin don ƙayyade yaduwar COVID-19 a cikin Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila, kuma an kwatanta shi da Italiya.
A cikin yanayin cutar COVID-19, muna la'akari da yanayin cutar COVID-19 na kwanaki 14, wanda ke haifar da ci gaban COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a cikin Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila, a lokacin daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Mun kuma ba da jimlar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a kowace ƙasa a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da ƙarfe 8:00 na safe, idan aka kwatanta da adadin Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yawan kamuwa da COVID-19 a Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da Ingila
Yanayin cutar COVID-19 na kwanaki 14 a cikin Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya zai kasance daidai da na lardin Hubei (China) (Figure 1).
Ga ƙasashen Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila, cutar COVID-19 ta fara fitowa a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu sannan ta fara fitowa a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (Ƙarin bayani).
Wannan ya kasance ne saboda yawan adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a Italiya, amma a duk ƙasashen Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai, yawan masu kamuwa da COVID-19 ya kasance daidai (Ƙarin Bayani).
Adadi na 2 ya nuna jimlar adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19, a cikin Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila idan aka kwatanta da Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Wannan yana nuna cewa, a ranar 15 ga Maris da ƙarfe 8:00 na safe, wasu ƙasashe 15 na Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila suna da adadin adadin masu cutar kamar Italiya makonni 3 ko ƙasa da haka da suka gabata.
Sakamakon bincikenmu ya nuna cewa yawan masu kamuwa da COVID-19 zai karu sosai a cikin Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila.
Bayanan da aka samu game da yawan masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 sun nuna cewa cutar ta yadu daidai a wasu ƙasashe.
Ko da yake akwai bambance-bambance a cikin ƙasashe, ƙwararrun likitoci za su iya ba da magani daban-daban, kuma a wasu lokuta ma'anar cututtuka ta bambanta tsakanin ƙasashe da ƙa'idodi don zaɓar marasa lafiya waɗanda za a gwada su don COVID-19, har ma da gwajin gaba.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitocin Italiya a cikin yankin sun ba da rahoton cewa kashi 10% na masu cutar COVID-19 suna buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ba da rahoton cewa asibitocin yankin suna cike da marasa lafiya.
Bayanai na asibiti da/ko kulawa mai tsanani na COVID-19 a halin yanzu suna samuwa a cikin Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai don kashi 6% da 1% na yawan jama'a (ba a nuna bayanai ba).
Duk da haka, dole ne a haɗa su da kyau don su dace da sabon bayanin da ya fi dacewa game da yawan masu cutar da mutuwar.
Wani bincike da aka yi a 2010-11 ya nuna canji mai yawa a cikin cibiyoyin kulawa da ke da tsananin kulawa da matsakaici a Turai, tare da gado 29.2 a Jamus da gada 4.2 ga kowane mutum 100,000 a Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe na iya samun ƙarin ko ƙasa da Italiya (12.5 cibiyoyin kulawa da ke da tsananin kulawa da matsakaitan gadaje ga kowane mutum 100,000 a 201011).
Inganta yanayin kula da marasa lafiya ya wuce likita, saboda ƙididdigar kusancin Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da Burtaniya dangane da yawan asibitocin COVID-19 da kuma &gt; 90% na haɗarin rashin gado a cikin ICU, an ba da su a cikin sabon tsarin ECDC na shida don kimanta haɗarin COVID-19.
Saboda yawan marasa lafiya a wasu sassan Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da Ingila, kuma asibitoci a cibiyoyin kulawa mai tsanani galibi ana amfani da su don ɗaukar yawan jama'a na yanki, dole ne a samar da bayanai game da cututtuka da gadajen kulawa mai tsanani a cikin wani yanki da ake kira Nomenclature of Level 2 Information Units (NUTS-2).
Bayanai na yanzu da na gaba daga Italiya da sauran ƙasashe sun nuna cewa cutar COVID-19 tana yaduwa cikin sauri a cikin Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila.
Kasashe, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa da hankali suna buƙatar shirya yadda za su magance ƙarin kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2 da kuma karuwar yawan masu cutar COVID-19 da ke neman magani, musamman a cikin cibiyoyin kulawa da hankali, kamar waɗanda ke cikin yankunan Italiya da ke fama da cutar.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin sabon binciken gaggawa na ECDC, ana buƙatar saurin, ingantaccen tsari da ingantaccen tsari don hana yaduwar SARS-COV-2, janye hankalin mutane daga kamuwa da cutar da kuma mai da hankali kan rage yawan kamuwa da cutar; saboda ƙididdigar yawan kamuwa da cutar ba zai taimaka wa yanke shawara ba kuma asibitoci ba za su sami lokacin fahimta, yarda da kuma shirya don kulawa ba idan ba a gwada su ba.
Binciken gaggawa na haɗarin zai kuma tattauna kan matakan kiwon lafiya na jama'a don rage yaduwar cutar.
Akwai ɗan gajeren lokaci a lokacin da ƙasashe ke da damar ƙara sarrafa ƙoƙarin da suke yi don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da matsa lamba kan likitoci.
Idan ba a yi hakan ba, cibiyoyin kiwon lafiya a wasu ƙasashen Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai za su sami ƙarin mutane da ke fama da cutar da za su bukaci kulawar mai tsanani a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar kwayar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wacce ke haifar da cutar sankarar bargo mai saurin kamuwa da cutar (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), ta riga ta kashe mutane sama da 3,000 kuma ta shafi mutane sama da 80,000 a China da sauran sassan duniya, wanda ya zama babbar barazana ga lafiyar ɗan adam.
A cikin yanayin da ya dace da cutar SARS-CoV, wanda ya haifar da dubban kamuwa da cutar SARS a 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya samo asali ne daga ƙuda kuma yana da alamun bayyanar cututtuka iri ɗaya da kuma kamuwa da cuta iri ɗaya.
Koyaya, COVID-19 ba ta da ƙarfi kuma ba ta da haɗari kamar SARS amma tana yaduwa sosai kuma tana shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa kuma tana shafar maza fiye da mata.
Yayin da wallafe-wallafen da ke tattare da cutar ke ci gaba da ƙaruwa, manufar wannan labarin shine samar da bayanai masu dacewa da kuma nazarin ayyukan bincike a wannan fannin.
Za a tattauna muhimman bayanai game da cututtuka, cututtuka masu tasowa, cututtuka, yadda za a gane su, yadda za a bi da su, yadda za a yi hasashen cutar, da kuma yadda za a kāre kansu.
Ko da yake akwai tambayoyi da yawa da ba a amsa ba tukuna, muna fatan wannan talifin zai taimaka maka ka san da kuma magance wannan muguwar cuta.
Bikin bazara na ranar 25 ga Janairun 2020 ya zama na musamman kuma abin tunawa ga duk Sinawa, saboda an hana su fita waje a duk lokacin bikin da kuma makonni da yawa bayan haka saboda barkewar cutar.
Wannan kwayar cutar tana da alaƙa da kwayar cutar coronavirus (CoV) wacce ta kasance cutar sauro mai saurin kamuwa da cuta (SARS) a cikin 2003; an sake ta da SARS-CoV-2 ta Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, kuma cutar da ta haifar da ita an sake ta da CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Cutar ta fara ne a birnin Wuhan na kasar Sin, kuma ta bazu cikin sauri a kasar Sin da kuma kusan ƙasashe 50 a duniya.
A ranar 2 ga Maris, 2020, cutar ta haifar da ƙarin kamuwa da COVID-19 sama da 80,000, tare da warkewa da sake dawowa sama da 40,000 da mutuwar sama da 3,000.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 shine "magabcin lamba 1 na ɗan adam" kuma yana iya zama mafi muni fiye da ta'addanci.
A cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), a cikin ƙasa da watanni biyu, mata sun buga labarai sama da 200 game da COVID-19 gami da ilimin ƙwayoyin cuta, cututtukan cututtuka, ilimin cututtuka, ganewar asali, da hanyoyin magani, tun lokacin da aka fara ba da rahoto a ranar 7 ga Janairu 2020 game da yadda cutar ke yaduwa.
Wannan talifin zai yi ƙoƙari ya taƙaita abin da za a yi a wannan sabon abu da ke yaɗuwa da sauri.
Idan za ta yiwu, za a gwada kwatancen COVID-19 da SARS da kuma cutar CoV, cutar murar Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS, wanda ya bayyana a cikin 2012).
Za mu kuma tattauna abin da muka koya game da yadda za a magance cutar da kuma yadda za a magance ta da kuma wasu tambayoyi masu muhimmanci.
An ce CoVs ba su da haɗari sosai, galibi suna haifar da 15% na yawan kamuwa da mura.
Duk da haka, a wannan karni, mun sami wasu CoVs masu cutar mutum sau biyu, kamar SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, waɗanda suka haifar da barkewar cutar daga China a 2003 da Saudi Arabiya a 2012, kuma sun bazu cikin sauri zuwa wasu ƙasashe tare da kamuwa da cuta da kashe mutane da yawa.
Saboda haka, COVID-19 na yanzu shine CoV na uku da ya bayyana a tarihin ɗan adam.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin adadi. An fara bayyana cutar ta numfashi mai lamba 1.1 a Wuhan a ranar 31 ga Fabrairun 2019 ta Hukumar Kula da Kiwon Lafiyar Jama'ar Sin.
