Ya kara da cewa, kuma wanene ba zai taɓa ganin annobar da za a iya kawo ƙarshen ta ba.
An kira wannan annoba bayan shawarar da Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta yanke a watan Janairu ta ayyana ta a matsayin babbar matsalar kiwon lafiya ta duniya.
