A ranar Alhamis, Rahoton Haɗin Kai ya ba da rahoton cewa daga cikin mutane 126,000 da aka gano da cutar COVID-19 a duniya, 4,600 sun mutu.
Cutar annobar coronavirus ta 2019-20 ita ce cutar sankarar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wanda cutar cututtukan numfashi ta coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) ta haifar.
An gano cutar a Wuhan, China, a watan Disamba na 2019, an bayyana ta a matsayin matsalar lafiyar jama'a a ranar 30 ga Janairu, 2020, kuma an ayyana ta a matsayin annoba a ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020.
A ranar 10 ga Afrilu, 2020, an sami mutane miliyan 1.61 da ke da cutar COVID-19 a cikin yankuna 210 da yankuna, wanda ya haifar da mutuwar mutane 97,000.
Mutane 364,000 sun bar gidajensu.
Yawan mace-mace ya kai kashi 4 cikin dari a China, kashi 13.04 cikin dari a Algeria da kashi 0.08 cikin dari a New Zealand.
