Angiotensin converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) wani enzyme ne wanda yake cikin ƙwayoyin cuta na ƙwayoyin cuta, jijiyoyi, zuciya, koda da hanji.
ACE2 yana hana aikin enzyme mai canza angiotensin (ACE) ta hanyar rage yawan angiotensin-II da haɓaka ang ((1-7) yana mai da shi magani mai ƙarfi don magance cututtukan zuciya. ACE2 kuma yana taimakawa wajen shiga cikin coronavirus.
An samo enzyme a jikin mutum da ake kira hACE2.
Angiotensin mai canzawa enzyme 2 shine enzyme wanda aka samo a cikin zinc a cikin endothelial da sauran ƙwayoyin halitta.
Protein ACE2 yana da N-terminal peptidase M2 da kuma C-terminal mai karɓar amino acid.
ACE2 ya zama nau'in membrane na furotin guda ɗaya, tare da aikinsa na enzyme a waje da ƙwayoyin halitta da sauran kwayoyin halitta.
Ƙungiyar ACE2 ta fito daga cikin ƙwayoyin cuta da kuma wani enzyme da ake kira sheddase, sannan furotin ya shiga cikin jini kuma ya fita daga cikin fitsari.
ACE2 yana cikin kwayoyin halitta da yawa: ACE2 yana haɗuwa da membrane na ƙwayoyin cuta na huhu na nau'in II na ƙwayoyin alveolarenterocytes na ƙananan hanji, jijiyoyi da jijiyoyin jini da ƙwayoyin jijiyoyin jiki masu sauƙi.
Ana kuma samun ACE2 mRNA a cikin ƙwayar ƙwayar cuta, striatum, hypothalamus, da kuma ƙwaƙwalwar ƙwaƙwalwa.
Aikin farko na aCE2 shine aikin ACE.
ACE yana haɗuwa da hormone na angiotensin I zuwa angiotensin II vasoconstriction.
ACE2 yana ɗaurewa zuwa amino acid phenylalanine na carboxyl-terminal a cikin angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-pPhe) kuma yana haɓaka shi cikin angiotensin (1-7), mai saurin jijiyoyin jini (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 kuma yana iya ɗaure kansa ga peptides da yawa kamar su [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, da ghrelin.
ACE2 kuma yana daidaita ƙuntatawa na membrane na amino acid mai tsaka tsaki wanda ke ɗaukar SLC6A19 kuma yana da cutar Hartnup.
A cikin ƙwayoyin cuta na transmembrane, ACE2 shine farkon hanyar shiga cikin kwayoyin cutar coronavirus, da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (kwayar cutar SARS); da SARS-CoV-2 (kwayar cutar COVID-19).
A cikin mafi kyawun yanayin, haɗuwa da ƙwayar furotin S1 na SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV2 zuwa enzyme ACE2 a saman sel zai haifar da endocytosis da sarrafa kwayar enzyme tare da ɗayan endosomes a cikin sel.
Wannan hanyar shiga tana buƙatar inganta furotin S tare da protease na serine TMPRSS2, wanda ke cikin binciken magani mai tasiri. Wannan ya sa wasu mutane suka rage ACE2, a cikin ƙwayoyin halitta, don ƙoƙarin magance kamuwa da cuta.
Koyaya, ƙananan ƙungiyoyin ilimi da shari'a sun ba da shawarar ci gaba da ACE da ake buƙata da kuma maganin ARB.
Wani bita na tsarin da nazarin meta da aka buga a ranar 11 ga Yuli, 2012 ya gano cewa Maganin ACE yana rage haɗarin cutar huhu da kashi 34%.
Amma, haɗarin ciwon huhu ya ragu a cikin mutanen da aka kula da ACE waɗanda ke da haɗarin kamuwa da ciwon huhu, kamar waɗanda ke da ciwon zuciya.
Hakanan maganin ACE yana da alaƙa da rage yawan mutuwar ciwon huhu, amma sakamakon bai yi tasiri sosai ba a cikin haɗarin ciwon huhu.
Abubuwan da ke tattare da mutum ACE2 (rhACE2) sabon magani ne don ciwon huhu, kuma an yi amfani da shi don magance cutar haemodynacy na huhu da kuma oxygenation a cikin aladu tare da lypopolysaccharemia a cikin ciwon huhu.
Rashin rayuwa na rhACE2 a cikin mutane shine awanni 10 kuma yana aiki a cikin minti 30 da rabi a cikin awanni 24.
Yawancin nazarin sun nuna cewa rhACE2 na iya zama magani mai tasiri ga masu hanawa na RAS (Renin-angiotensin inhibitors) ko kuma masu cutar angiotensin mai tsanani. rhACE2 ana nazarin asibiti don magance cututtukan numfashi.
